\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Rom 12:3; 12:6; 1 Korin 12:11\x*E fo, Krais vaghvagha bar en apangkufi. Egha kamagh…®ra uan apangkuvir ekiam…®n abaragha an m…®rara, a bizir bar aghuim vaghvagha e gan…®ngi.
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Onger Akaba 68:18; Kolosi 2:15\x*God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme:
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúA bar p…®n ghuavanabogha,
\q2 kalabuziar gumazir av…®rim iniz…®,
\q3 me a ko ghue.
\q1 Egha bizir bar aghuiba
\q2 pura gumazamizibagh an…®ngi.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt Jon 3:13\x*Akar kam, ‚ÄúA ghuavanabo,‚Äù a kamagh…®n en akaz…® e fo, Krais a faragha nguazir bar v…®n mar itim giraghu.\f + \fr 4:9 \ft Fofozir gumazir maba, akar kam giragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA faragha nguazir kam bar an v…®n izaghir…®.‚Äù\f*
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Hibru 4:14; 9:24\x*Egha gumazir faragha iraghuzir kam, a uaghan p…®n ghuavanaga, uab…® is…® biziba bar dagh iz…®vaghasa, kamagh…®n an overiar bar p…®n itim…®n ghuavanabo.
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Rom 12:7; 1 Korin 12:28; 2 Timoti 4:5\x*Gumazir kamra a ‚Äúbizir bar aghuiba pura gumazamizibagh an…®ngi.‚Äù A bizir aghuir kaba me gan…®ngi, marazi an aposel…®n ingangarim me gan…®ngi. Marazi, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n ingangarim me gan…®ngi. Marazi, a God…®n Akar Aghuim akunamin ingangarim me gan…®ngi, marasi, a God…®n gumazamizibar ganamin ingangarim me gan…®ngi, egha marasi, gumazamiziba God ifongezir arazibar men sure damuamin ingangarim me gan…®ngi.
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt 1 Korin 12:7; Efesus 1:23; 2 Timoti 3:17\x*Krais kamagh…®n ifonge, e God…®n gumazamiziba a en akuraght…® e a bagh ingangarir aghuibar amuam. Eght…® kamagh…®n e Krais…®n inivaf…®zim…®n otogh gavgavigh derav…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n a bizir aghuir kaba e gan…®ngi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt 1 Korin 14:20; Kolosi 1:28; 2:2\x*Eght…® ingangarir kam mamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® en n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bar gavgavight…® bizir kam e damut…® e bar mogh…®ra navir vam…®ra ikiamin arazim inigh, egh God…®n Otarim guizbang…®ra bar a g…®fogham. Kamagh…®n damight…® e Krais…®n g…®n zuir darorir kam…®n aven, e tugh gavgavigh aghung mang…®, gumazir aruabar avagh…®va e guizbang…®ra Krais…®n m…®n otogham.
