\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Aisaia 28:9; 1 Korin 14:20; 2 Korin 2:17; Hibru 13:9\x*E ua boribar m…®n ikian kogham. Ia fo, gumazir ifavariba, me gumazamizibagh ifara me gamima me tuavir kurabar zui. Eght…® men m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ifavariba uaghan ia munamangan kogham, mati ongarim ko am…®nim kurim givai.
\v 15 \x - \xo 4:15 \xt Efesus 1:22; 4:25; Kolosi 1:18; 1 Jon 3:18\x*E men m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ifavariba baraghan kogham. E igharaz darazigh ifongezir arazim damuva guiz…®n akabar me m…®k…®mam. Egh e Krais…®n m…®rara aghung…®va a ko porogh…®v ik…®t…® a en dapanim…®n ikiam.
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Kolosi 2:19\x*A en dapanim…®n itima en soroghafariba ko damaziba ko inivaf…®zim…®n bizir maba sara dar m…®n iti. Egha an e gamima e inivaf…®zim…®n aven bar uari isavsuira. Ez…® mati inivaf…®zim…®n aven itir tevir ag…®riba ko aghariba uari isavsuighiz…® mogh…®n, an e gamima e uari isavsuiki, egha bar uarigh ifongezir arazim gami. E vaghvagha uan ingangarir aghuim gamua, kamagh…®n inivaf…®zir kam uab…® aghua ghua gavgafi.
\s1 Krais…®n adarazi arazir igiabar g…®nt…®gh
