\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Rom 1:21; 1 Pita 1:14\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ekiam…®n ziam…®n akar mam pamtem kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa. Ia uam gumazir Ekiam g…®fozir puvat…®zibar arazibar g…®nt…®ghan mark…®. Men n…®ghn…®ziba, m…®ngariba puvat…®.
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Aposel 26:18; Galesia 4:8; Efesus 2:12; 1 Tesalonika 4:5\x*Egha men n…®ghn…®ziba mati me m…®tatem…®n iti. Egha me fofoziba bar puvat…®gha men naviba bar gavgafi, kamagh…®n me God…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n azenan iti.
\v 19 \x - \xo 4:19 \xt Kolosi 3:5\x*Me arazir kurabagh amuav…®ra ikiava dat…®r…®gh…®n uam aghums…®ziba puvat…®. Me bar uari isa arazir kurabagh anigh arazir m…®z…®r…®zir av…®rir igharazibar amus…® bizitam men suiraghan kogham.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® k…® ghaze, ia Krais…®n guiz…®n akam baraghizir dughiam…®n, me bizir kurar kabar ian sure gamizir puvat…®.
\v 21 Ia guizbang…®ra Krais…®n akam baregha g…®fa. Ez…® ia an g…®n zuir darasi, me guiz…®n akam…®n ian sure gamigha g…®fa. Guiz…®n akar kam, a Iesus…®n aven iti.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 4:22 \xt Rom 6:6; 8:13; Efesus 2:2-3; 4:17; Kolosi 3:9; Hibru 12:1; 1 Pita 4:3\x*Ia fom…®ra uan navir ghuribar arazibar g…®n zuima da ia gamima ia arazir ifavariba ko arazir kurabar amuasa navim d…®kavava, ia gas…®ghas…®si. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia navir ghurim ategh…®va mati gumazim korotiar ghurim sue.
\v 23 \x - \xo 4:23 \xt Rom 12:2; Kolosi 3:10\x*Ian n…®ghn…®ziba ko navibagh igh…®ghiregh bar igiabar otifigh.
\v 24 \x - \xo 4:24 \xt Jenesis 1:26; Rom 6:4; Efesus 2:10; Kolosi 3:10\x*Ia navir igiaba inigh mati gumazim korotiar igiam aru. God uab…® navir igiar ian aven itibagh amiz…® ia an m…®n otifi. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar ian gan fogham, ia God…®n damazim…®n deragha a baghav…®ra iti.
