\v 25 \x - \xo 4:25 \xt Sekaraia 8:16; Rom 12:5; Kolosi 3:8-9\x*Kamagh…®n ia ifavarir arazim atakigh. E bar mogh…®ra Krais…®n inivaf…®zim…®n soroghafariba ko an bizibar m…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia bar mogh…®rama guiz…®n akabar gumazamizir igharazibav k…®m.
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 4:26 \xt Onger Akaba 4:4; Jems 1:19-20\x*Ia atar…®va, uari bagh gan egh arazir kuratam damighan kogham. Ian adarim ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® am…®nim p…®ran mark…®.
