\v 28 \x - \xo 4:28 \xt 1 Tesalonika 4:11; 2 Tesalonika 3:8; 3:11-12\x*Ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba uam ok…®man mark…®. Me uari uan dafaribar ingangarir aghuibar amu. Egh uaghan gumazamizir onganarazibar akurvaghs…®, ingar…®va bizitaba inigh me dan…®ng.
