\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29 \xt Efesus 5:4; Kolosi 3:8; 3:16; 4:6; 1 Tesalonika 5:11\x*Eght…® akar m…®z…®r…®zir kuraba ian akabar otivan mark…®. Ia gumazamizibar akurvaghamin akabara m…®k…®m. Akar aghuir igharaz darazi gavgavim me dan…®ngamibara, da ian akabar otiv. Egh akar ia m…®geir kaba, da gumazamizir ia barazibar akurvagham.
