\v 30 \x - \xo 4:30 \xt Aisaia 63:10; Rom 8:23; Efesus 1:13-14; 1 Tesalonika 5:19\x*Eght…® ia God…®n Duam os…®mt…®zim a dan…®ngan mark…®. Ia fo, God ia an gumazamizibar otivasa, a uan Duam ia gan…®ngi. Eght…® a ian akaght…® ia fogh suam, ia guizbang…®ra an gumazamizibara, egh dughiar a uam ia iniamim…®n a ia damight…® ia bar f…®righ…®regham.
\v 31 \x - \xo 4:31 \xt Kolosi 3:8; 3:18-19; Taitus 3:2-3; 1 Pita 2:1\x*Ia arazir kurar kaba atakigh: navir kurar igharazi tav…®n itir arazim, ko an…®ngagharim, ko adarir arazim, ko pamtem dagarvagha uari adoghodozir arazim, ko akar kuraba uari gasir arazim, ko igharaz darazir aghuaghuazir arazir maba sara.
\v 32 \x - \xo 4:32 \xt Matyu 6:14; 18:22-35; Mak 11:25; 2 Korin 2:10; Kolosi 3:13\x*Egh ia arazir aghuibar Krais…®n adarazi me damu, men apangkuv. Egh uaghan uari uan arazir kuraba g…®n amang, mati God Krais…®n ingangarim…®n tuavim…®n, ian arazir kuraba g…®n amadi.
\c 5
\s1 E angazangarim…®n aven daruam
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Matyu 5:48; Luk 6:36\x*Ia God bar ifongezir boriba, kamagh…®n ia an amir arazibar g…®n mang…®.
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 29:18; Ofa Gami 1:9; Onger Akaba 40:6; Jon 13:34; Rom 14:15; 2 Korin 2:15; Galesia 2:20; Hibru 7:27; 10:10; 1 Jon 3:11; 3:23\x*Ian arazir ia amiba, arazir gumazamizibagh ifongezir arazim gis…®n tugh, mati Krais bar e gifuegha e bagha uab…® anigha areme. Kamagh…®n an ovevem mati ofan mughuriar aghuir God ifongezim.
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Rom 6:13; 1 Korin 5:1; 2 Korin 12:21; Kolosi 3:5; 1 Tesalonika 4:3\x*Ia God…®n gumazamizibara. Kamagh…®n ia, gumazamiziba tintiniba uari bak…®a uari isava akuir arazim, ko arazir m…®z…®r…®ziba, ko igharaz darazir bizibar gan…®va da ifongamin araziba, ia arazir kabar amuan mark…®. Egh uaghan arazir kabar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba tong ian tong…®n otivan mark…®.
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Matyu 12:35; Rom 1:28; Efesus 4:29\x*Egh ia akar m…®z…®r…®ziba ko akar onganiba ko asuir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kurabar amuan mark…®. Kar uaghan ia damuamin araziba puvat…®. Arazir ia damuamimra kara, ia God m…®nab…®.
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt 1 Korin 6:9-10; Galesia 5:19-21; Kolosi 3:5\x*Ia kamagh…®n fogh, gumazamizir tintiniba uari isava akuir arazim gamiba, ko gumazamizir arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amiba, ko gumazamizir marazir bizibar gara ifuer arazim gamiba, (arazir kam mati ia uari isa God gan…®di mogh…®n ia uari isa bizir ifongezibagh an…®di), ez…® gumazamizir kamagh…®n amiba, me God ko Krais Ativir Gumazamizibar tong…®n ikian kogham.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Rom 1:18; Kolosi 2:4; 2:8; 2 Tesalonika 2:3\x*Ia tav ateght…® a ia gifar ia damut…®, ia akar ifavaribar g…®n mangan mark…®. Arazir kurar kaba bagh God…®n an…®ngagharim gumazamizir an akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®ziba me bativam.
\v 7 Kamagh…®n, ia ifavarir gumazir kaba tong men poghan mark…®.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Jon 12:36; Aposel 26:18; Rom 1:21; 2 Korin 3:18; Efesus 2:11-13; Kolosi 1:13; 1 Pita 2:9; 1 Jon 2:9\x*Ia faragha m…®tatem…®n aven ike, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ia Ekiam…®n gumazamizibar otivigha, angazangarim…®n aven iti. Kamagh…®n ia gumazamizir angazangarim…®n aven itibar m…®n daru.
